name: Knockout - Edgar Allan
description:
Knockout is an end-to-end development framework that helps designers and Webflow developers accomplish more together. Our companion Figma template standardizes spacing based on Knockout's fully responsive native grid. Design and build are aligned from the get-go, and designers are empowered to create dev-ready assets that work seamlessly with our class library.


See something weird? Let us know!
